<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10706</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西很快跑出玛拉家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20354</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“听着，朋友们。”她说，“我得......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“练习扔飞盘？”特勒尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24861</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31067</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他再一次把飞盘扔向了罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37220</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈哈！”飞盘掉在草地上，罗西假笑了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37221</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40162</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得先回家了。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40163</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我忘了......嗯......喂我的金鱼！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55387</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西很快就飞到了美罗城的上空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60494</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>西街上到处都是毁坏的汽车和公交车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60495</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看到街上到处都有巨大的脚印。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看上去像是一只大蜥蜴留下的脚印。”罗西想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73354</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探站在一堆砖头旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>砖头上面有一个坏了的牌子，上面写着“快捷超市”。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85354</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西微笑着说：“您为什么把‘快捷超市’推倒了，侦探先生？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是他们把咖啡都卖完了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很有意思，火箭女孩儿。”史密斯侦探皱着眉头，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是我推倒的‘快捷超市’。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是一个巨大的怪物踩了它。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108604</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114278</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看了看四周。“我看到了怪物的脚印。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114279</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不过，它现在在哪儿呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117247</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121604</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>侦探耸耸肩。“我刚到这里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121605</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我来的时候，怪物已经不见了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125487</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133588</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个女人跑过来。“那个怪物往南走了。”她指着街道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133589</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看了一下对面的街道，叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146504</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是一个园丁，来这个公共花园除草，但是现在全毁了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146505</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150945</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的车也毁了！”一个男人生气地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150946</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他走向史密斯侦探和罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154904</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158414</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怪物踩坏了我的车！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158415</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163741</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怪物踩坏了我的公交车！”公交车司机说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163742</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169573</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>又一个男人跑过来。“真是太气人了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169574</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177801</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个怪物把我花店的屋顶掀开了，吃光了我所有的花！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182479</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个怪物吃花？”史密斯侦探问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182480</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拿出笔记本，开始写。园丁眨了眨眼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188354</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也看到了，那怪物吃光了花园里所有的花。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193354</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197359</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>开花店的男人仍然很生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197360</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202240</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看向罗西。“你打算怎么办，火箭女孩儿？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202241</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西举起双手。“放心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我会找到那个怪物，阻止它的。”她看着园丁，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说那个怪物往南走了，对吧？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215330</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”园丁说，“就是美罗城会展中心那边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226813</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>本来我是打算要去那儿......”她咽了一口口水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226814</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229600</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么了？”罗西问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229601</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道那只怪物为什么去会展中心了。”园丁说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天那里有个很大的花展！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>